{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "\u00a31000 fine for loud exhaust pipes & seize vehicles of repeat offenders",
        "additional_details": "We think there is a current trend amongst a small but significant proportion of road users to fit excessively loud, anti-social & illegally modified exhaust pipes onto their vehicles.\r\n \r\nWe think the present penalties aren't working effectively at curbing the problem and need to be increased to discourage users from breaking the existing legislation.\r\n \r\nWe think these modified exhaust pipes also encourage speeding and dangerous driving due to the driver often trying to create a 'desirable noise' under hard acceleration.",
        "background": "Increase the on the spot fine from \u00a350 to \u00a31000 for any motor vehicle being used on a public highway with an illegally loud & modified exhaust system.\r\n\r\nTo seize and destroy the vehicles of repeat offenders.\r\n",
